  "instructions": [
    "in a large bowl, combine hominy and water to soak overnight",
    "drain and rinse the hominy, then mash in a blender until smooth",
    "in a large skillet, heat oil over medium and sauté onion and garlic until softened",
    "add cumin, chili powder, and salt to the skillet and cook for 1 minute",
    "stir in the mashed hominy and cook for 2-3 minutes",
    "preheat a tava or griddle to medium-high heat",
    "divide the hominy mixture into 4-6 portions, shape into flat circles",
    "place the huaraches on the preheated tava, cook for 2-3 minutes on each side",
    "wrap the huaraches in large corn tortillas and steam on a tava or steamer basket",
    "top with grilled onions, figs, and a sprinkle of salt"
